      • AcraReport

        public AcraReport(com.google.gdata.data.spreadsheet.CustomElementCollection pCustomElements)
        Constructor.

        Wraps the given spreadsheet list entry and provides read only access to report field values.

        Parameters:
        pCustomElements - custom element collection of a Google Spreadsheet list entry
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - the given ListEntry havn't all AcraReportHeader tag values,
        unable to parse the crash date from the ACRA report
